Answ. Yes, against that shall the Scripture bear witness;
the book of Nathan the Prophet, the book of Ahaijah, the book of Iddo, 2 Chr. 9. 29. the book of Shemaia, 2 Chr. 20. 15. the book of Gad, 1 Chro. 29. 29. the book of Jehu, 2 Chro. 20. 3 • . the book of Jasher, 2 Sam. 1. 18. the Prophesie of Enoch, Jud.
• . one Epistle of the Corinthians, 1 Cor. 3. 9. one Epistle to the Ephesians, Eph. 3. 3. one Epistle to the Laodiceans. Col. 4. All these Scriptures were given forth from the same Spirit, and to the same end and use, as those are, which are bound up in the Scriptures, although these be left out.
